parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine light to illuminate, leading to engine stalling, loss of power, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine light is illuminated on the instrument panel
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle pulls to one side while accelerating
the vehicle has a rough idle
the vehicle has a decreased fuel efficiency.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to fail, leading to costly repairs, loss of vehicle use, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine fails
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the timing chain fractures
the vehicle has a rough idle
the vehicle has a decreased fuel efficiency.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealers to properly diagnose and repair issues related to the camshaft position sensor and timing chain can lead to further damage to the vehicle, loss of vehicle use, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Dealers refuse to perform recall repairs
dealers misdiagnose issues
dealers charge for unnecessary repairs
dealers fail to correct issues after multiple attempts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine fires can cause complete destruction of the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Engine fire
vehicle destruction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to have the airbag recall repair performed can leave the vehicle in a potentially unsafe condition, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Difficulty in scheduling or having the airbag recall repair performed
unresponsive or unhelpful customer service
lack of available dealerships to perform the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unresponsive or unhelpful customer service can lead to frustration and delay in addressing safety concerns, potentially leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition.
symptoms: Difficulty in reaching a customer service representative
unhelpful or unresponsive customer service
long wait times or hold times.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Limited Dealership Availability for Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Limited availability of dealerships to perform recall repairs can lead to delays or inability to have the repair performed, potentially leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition.
symptoms: Difficulty in finding a dealership to perform the recall repair
limited dealership availability
long wait times for the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hose can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to a decrease in braking performance, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
brake fluid leak
reduced braking performance
increased stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to obtain recall repair can leave the vehicle in an unsafe condition, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Dealer not in operation
unable to schedule recall repair
recall repair not available.
